PROJECTS TAKEN.Description:
Developed an outlook add-in for Trello that has been released on office store. This add-in enables user to create trello cards from the mail. The default card title is mail subject while the mail body is set as card description. Due date can also be  added to the card. 
The add-in was released as MVP when add-ins were launched for outlook on iOS

PROJECTS TAKEN.Title of Project: Profit Maximization in Sponsored Search Auctions
PROJECTS TAKEN.Description: The project suggests an algorithm for search engines(say Google) to maximize the profit without compromising with its user friendliness
